{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":88,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"什么事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":1,"line_start":26,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"没有什么，只不过走错路了。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":1,"line_start":30,"line_end":30},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"你又走错了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":1,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"我……我……","tone":"痛苦","chapter":1,"line_start":46,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"你又何苦瞒我？我早已知道了。","tone":"温柔","chapter":1,"line_start":48,"line_end":48},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"你早已知道了？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":1,"line_start":50,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"我方才听见那声鸡啼，便已猜出必定是'十二星相'中人找上咱们了，你怕我担心，所以才瞒着我，是么？","tone":"温柔","chapter":1,"line_start":52,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"奇怪……你我此行如此秘密，他们怎会知道？但……但你只管放心，什么事都有我来抵挡！","tone":"认真","chapter":1,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"你又错了，自从那天……那天我准备和你共生共死，无论有什么危险患难，也该由咱们俩共同承当。","tone":"柔声","chapter":1,"line_start":56,"line_end":56},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"但你现在……","tone":"担心","chapter":1,"line_start":58,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"没关系，现在我觉得很好。","tone":"平静","chapter":1,"line_start":60,"line_end":60},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"好，你还能下车走么？道路两头都已有警兆，看来咱们也只有弃下车马，穿过这一片荒野……","tone":"焦急","chapter":1,"line_start":62,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"为什么要弃下车马呢？他们既已盯上咱们，反正已难脱身，倒不如就在这里等着，'十二星相'虽然有凶名，但咱们也未必怕他们！","tone":"认真","chapter":1,"line_start":64,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"我……我只是怕你……","tone":"担心","chapter":1,"line_start":66,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"你放心，我没关系。","tone":"温柔","chapter":1,"line_start":68,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"我能找着你，真是最幸运的事。","tone":"温柔","chapter":1,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"幸运的该是我才对，我知道，江湖中不知道有多少女孩子在羡慕我，妒忌我，只是她们……","tone":"微笑","chapter":1,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":null,"text":"他们似已来了！","tone":"恐惧","chapter":1,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":null,"text":"谁？！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":1,"line_start":88,"line_end":88}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_jiang_feng","name":"江枫","alias":["玉郎"],"identity":"天下第一美男子，出身豪富世家","faction":"无","role":"protagonist","archetype":"scholar","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"江湖第一美男子，为躲避移花宫追杀携妻出逃","personality":{"traits":["风流倜傥","温文尔雅","深情","勇敢","果断"],"speech_style":"温文尔雅，言辞得体","temperament":"风流蕴藉"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_che_zhong_nv","type":"恋人","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"生死与共"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[1],"source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":2,"line_end":4,"text":"江枫和燕南天这两人的名字"}]},{"id":"char_che_xiang_zhong_ren","name":"车厢中人","alias":["少妇"],"identity":"移花宫叛逃宫女，身怀六甲","faction":"移花宫","role":"companion","archetype":"healer","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"移花宫叛逃者，怀有双胞胎，掌握移花接玉绝技","personality":{"traits":["温柔","坚毅","智慧","勇敢","深沉"],"speech_style":"甜美温柔，语声轻柔","temperament":"温柔而坚定"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_jiang_feng","type":"恋人","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"生死与共"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[1],"source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":24,"line_end":26,"text":"车厢中却有个甜美而温柔的语声问道"}]},{"id":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","name":"红衣鸡冠","alias":["司晨客","鸡冠人"],"identity":"十二星相之首，绰号司晨客","faction":"十二星相","role":"villain","archetype":"assassin","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"十二星相中司晨客，身着火红衣裳，使钢啄","personality":{"traits":["诡秘","狠辣","狡猾","贪婪","残忍"],"speech_style":"嗄嗄怪笑，尖锐刺耳","temperament":"阴险狡诈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_hei_mian_jun","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"同伙"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[1],"source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":92,"line_end":92,"text":"第一个人，身长不足五尺，瘦小枯干，却穿着一身火红的衣裳"}]},{"id":"char_huang_yi_ji_xiong","name":"黄衣鸡胸","alias":[],"identity":"十二星相成员，使双快刀","faction":"十二星相","role":"villain","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"十二星相中鸡胸，黄衣黄冠，满脸横肉，使双快刀","personality":{"traits":["凶悍","沉默","冷酷","凶猛","果断"],"speech_style":"少言寡语","temperament":"冷酷凶悍"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"同伙"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[1],"source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":93,"line_end":93,"text":"第二个人，身长却赫然在九尺开外，高大魁伟，黄衣黄冠"}]},{"id":"char_hua_yi_ji_wei","name":"花衣鸡尾","alias":[],"identity":"十二星相成员，使鸡爪镰，四人协同行动","faction":"十二星相","role":"villain","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"十二星相中四名鸡尾，穿五彩绸缎富贵衣，使鸡爪镰","personality":{"traits":["凶狠","协同","剽悍","凶猛","忠诚"],"speech_style":"寡言","temperament":"凶悍"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","type":"合作者","intensity":55,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"同伙"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[1],"source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":94,"line_end":96,"text":"后面跟着四个人打扮得更是奇怪，衣服竟是一块块五颜六色的绸缎缝成的"}]},{"id":"char_hei_mian_jun","name":"黑面君","alias":[],"identity":"十二星相成员，身材极胖","faction":"十二星相","role":"villain","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"十二星相中黑面君，极胖，使拳法，行动蹒跚但身法轻灵","personality":{"traits":["贪婪","好色","残忍","狡猾","虚张声势"],"speech_style":"哈哈大笑，言语粗俗","temperament":"贪婪残忍"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"同伙"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[1],"source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":98,"line_end":100,"text":"还有个人远远跟在后面……胖得实在已快走不动了"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_shi_er_xing_xiang","name":"十二星相","type":"帮派","location":"江湖各地","sub_divisions":["司晨客","黑面君","鸡胸","鸡尾"],"one_line":"江湖凶名昭著的盗匪团伙，以十二生肖为号，贼不空手","source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":52,"line_end":52,"text":"'十二星相'中人找上咱们了"}]}],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":89,"line_end":183,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","speaker_name":"红衣人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"不错，咱们已来了！","tone":"大笑","chapter":1,"line_start":83,"line_end":85},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","text":"来的可是'十二星相'中之司晨客与黑面君么？","tone":"认真","chapter":1,"line_start":104,"line_end":104},{"speaker":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","speaker_name":"红衣人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"江公子果然好眼力，但咱们不过是一只鸡、一只猪而已，司晨客、黑面君，这些好听的名字，不过是江湖中人胡乱取的，咱们承当不起。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":1,"line_start":106,"line_end":108},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","text":"阁下想必就是……","tone":"疑问","chapter":1,"line_start":110,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","speaker_name":"红衣人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"红的是鸡冠，黄的是鸡胸，花的是鸡尾，至于后面那位，你瞧他模样像什么，他就是什么。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":1,"line_start":112,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","text":"几位不知有何见教？","tone":"疑问","chapter":1,"line_start":116,"line_end":116},{"speaker":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","speaker_name":"红衣鸡冠","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"闻得江公子有了新宠，咱兄弟都忍不住想来瞧瞧这位能令玉郎动心的美人儿究竟美到什么地步，再者，咱兄弟还想来向公子讨件东西。","tone":"陈述","chapter":1,"line_start":118,"line_end":118},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","text":"只可惜在下此次匆匆出门，身无长物，哪有什么好东西，能人得了诸位名家法眼。","tone":"沉声","chapter":1,"line_start":120,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","speaker_name":"鸡冠人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"江公子此刻突然将家财完全变卖，咱们虽不知为的是什么，却也不想知道，但江公子以田庄换来的那袋明珠……嘿嘿，江公子也该知道咱们'十二星相'向来贼不空手，公子就把那袋明珠赏给咱们吧。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":1,"line_start":124,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","text":"好，好，原来你们倒竟已打听得如此清楚，在下也知道'十二星相'从来不轻易出手，出手后从不空回，但……","tone":"大笑","chapter":1,"line_start":128,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","speaker_name":"鸡冠人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"但什么？你不答应？","tone":"疑问","chapter":1,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","text":"若要我答应，只有……","tone":"冷笑","chapter":1,"line_start":134,"line_end":136},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","text":"哥儿们，加加油，咱们可不是女人，可莫要对这小子生出怜香惜玉的心，兄弟我且先去瞧瞧车子里的小美人儿。","tone":"大笑","chapter":1,"line_start":148,"line_end":150},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hei_mian_jun","text":"站住！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":1,"line_start":152,"line_end":152},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":null,"text":"你们瞧瞧这是什么？","tone":"淡然","chapter":1,"line_start":162,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":null,"text":"绣玉谷，移花宫。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":1,"line_start":168,"line_end":168},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":"char_hei_mian_jun","text":"你的眼力倒也不错。","tone":"淡然","chapter":1,"line_start":170,"line_end":170},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"我……小人。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":1,"line_start":172,"line_end":172},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":null,"text":"你们想不想死？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":1,"line_start":176,"line_end":176},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"小人，不……","tone":"恐惧","chapter":1,"line_start":178,"line_end":178},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":null,"text":"不想死的还不走！","tone":"厉声","chapter":1,"line_start":180,"line_end":180}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[{"id":"skill_yi_hua_jie_yu","name":"移花接玉","type":"掌法","faction":"移花宫","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"移花宫绝学，以柔克刚，借力打力，神鬼莫敌","techniques":[{"id":"tech_yi_hua_jie_yu","name":"移花接玉","type":"defense","description":"以柔克刚的高深武学，能将对手攻击借力打力返还，令敌人自伤"}],"progression":"出神入化","effects":["借力打力","反伤"],"combat_style":"以柔克刚","rag_refs":[1],"source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":226,"line_end":226,"text":"移花接玉，神鬼莫敌"}]},{"id":"skill_ji_zhua_lian","name":"鸡爪镰","type":"暗器","faction":"十二星相","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"十二星相花衣鸡尾使用的奇形外门兵刃","techniques":[{"id":"tech_ji_zhua_lian","name":"鸡爪镰","type":"attack","description":"形如鸡爪的镰刀，配合无间，攻击时锐不可挡，防守时密如蛛网"}],"progression":"登堂入室","effects":["攻击","防守"],"combat_style":"多人配合","rag_refs":[1],"source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":142,"line_end":144,"text":"三对鸡爪镰在地上等着"}]},{"id":"skill_ji_zhuo_mi","name":"鸡啄米","type":"指法","faction":"十二星相","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"红衣鸡冠使用的奇诡招式，如公鸡啄米般攻击要穴","techniques":[{"id":"tech_ji_zhuo_mi","name":"鸡啄米","type":"attack","description":"以钢啄为兵器，沿经脉要穴一路啄下的诡异招式"}],"progression":"炉火纯青","effects":["攻击要穴"],"combat_style":"诡速","rag_refs":[1],"source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":140,"line_end":140,"text":"看来正如公鸡啄米一般"}]}],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[{"id":"loc_xiu_yu_gu","name":"绣玉谷","region":"江湖","one_line":"移花宫所在地，江湖中令人闻之色变的神秘谷地","source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":168,"line_end":168,"text":"绣玉谷，移花宫"}]}],"items":[{"id":"item_mo_yu_mei_hua","name":"墨玉梅花","type":"special","owner":"char_che_zhong_nv","one_line":"移花宫信物，黑色梅花，出示即可震慑江湖凶徒","description":"一朵黑色的梅花，以墨玉雕琢而成，盛夏中出现已属奇事，黑梅花乃移花宫信物，见此花者如见移花宫主，江湖凶徒闻之色变","effects":["震慑","身份象征"],"origin":"移花宫","rarity":"稀世珍品","related_characters":["char_che_zhong_nv"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[1],"source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":156,"line_end":160,"text":"一只白生生的玉手……挟着枝梅花。黑色的梅花！"}]}]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_che_xiang_zhong_ren","updates":{"name":"少妇","source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":210,"line_end":210,"text":"车厢里坐着的乃是个云鬓蓬乱，面带病容的妇人"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":184,"line_end":283,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"你……你没事么？","tone":"担心","chapter":1,"line_start":184,"line_end":184},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"我只不过招了招手而已。","tone":"平静","chapter":1,"line_start":186,"line_end":188},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"不想你竟从宫中带出了朵墨玉梅花，连'十二星相'这样的凶人，竟也对她们如此惧怕。","tone":"无奈","chapter":1,"line_start":190,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"由此你就可想到她们有多可怕，咱们还是快走吧，别的人来了都不要紧，但若是……","tone":"焦急","chapter":1,"line_start":194,"line_end":194},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":null,"text":"咱们险些上当了，车子里若真是'移花宫'中的人，方才还能活着走么？你几时听说过'移花宫'手下留得有活口？","tone":"大笑","chapter":1,"line_start":198,"line_end":200},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"车厢中人","listener":"char_hei_mian_jun","text":"我饶了你，你竟还……","tone":"愤怒","chapter":1,"line_start":202,"line_end":202},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"冒牌货，出来吧！","tone":"厉声","chapter":1,"line_start":204,"line_end":206},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"原来是个大肚婆娘，居然还敢冒充移花宫的……","tone":"大笑","chapter":1,"line_start":214,"line_end":216},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"少妇","listener":"char_hei_mian_jun","text":"这大肚婆如何？","tone":"轻笑","chapter":1,"line_start":220,"line_end":222},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"暗算偷袭，又算得什么？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":1,"line_start":224,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":null,"text":"移花接玉，神鬼莫敌……","tone":"颤声","chapter":1,"line_start":230,"line_end":232},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"少妇","listener":"char_hei_mian_jun","text":"你既然知道，便也该知道我是不是冒充的。","tone":"淡然","chapter":1,"line_start":234,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"小……小人该死、该死……","tone":"恐惧","chapter":1,"line_start":236,"line_end":236},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"少妇","listener":"char_hei_mian_jun","text":"我要为孩子积点阴德，你们……你们快走吧。","tone":"无奈","chapter":1,"line_start":238,"line_end":238},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"幸亏你还有这一手，又将他们骇住，否则……","tone":"无奈","chapter":1,"line_start":242,"line_end":244},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"你怎么了？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":1,"line_start":248,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"少妇","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"我……我动了胎气……只怕……只怕已……快要……","tone":"痛苦","chapter":1,"line_start":250,"line_end":250},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"这如何是好？","tone":"焦急","chapter":1,"line_start":252,"line_end":252},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"少妇","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"你快将车子赶到路旁……快……快……快！","tone":"焦急","chapter":1,"line_start":254,"line_end":254},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":null,"text":"两个……是双胞胎……","tone":"欣喜","chapter":1,"line_start":262,"line_end":262},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hei_mian_jun","text":"你……你们又回来了？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":1,"line_start":268,"line_end":270},{"speaker":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","speaker_name":"鸡冠人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"公子吃惊了么？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":1,"line_start":272,"line_end":274},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","text":"你们莫非要来送死不成？！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":1,"line_start":276,"line_end":278},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"送死……","tone":"大笑","chapter":1,"line_start":280,"line_end":282}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_yi_hua_gong","name":"移花宫","type":"武林门派","location":"绣玉谷","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"江湖中最神秘恐怖的门派，以移花接玉绝技威震天下，宫主心狠手辣，令人闻风丧胆","source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":168,"line_end":168,"text":"绣玉谷，移花宫。"},{"chapter":1,"line_start":298,"line_end":298,"text":"现在车子里的，不过是移花宫的宫女、丫头"}]}],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_che_xiang_zhong_ren","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":210,"line_end":212,"text":"车厢里坐着的乃是个云鬓蓬乱，面带病容的妇人，却仍掩不住她的天香国色……只是她的腹部却高高隆起，原来竟已身怀六甲。"},{"chapter":1,"line_start":260,"line_end":262,"text":"大约数盏茶的时间，车厢中突然传出婴儿嘹亮的哭声。过了半晌，又听到江枫狂喜欢呼道：两个……是双胞胎……"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":284,"line_end":370,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hei_mian_jun","text":"瞧你们并非孤陋寡闻之辈，绣玉谷，移花宫的厉害，你们难道不知道？","tone":"厉声","chapter":1,"line_start":284,"line_end":286},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"姓江的，你还装什么蒜？你知道，我也知道，移花宫两位宫主，此刻想要的是你们两人的命，可不是我们。","tone":"大笑","chapter":1,"line_start":290,"line_end":292},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hei_mian_jun","text":"我瞧你倒真是疯子，移花宫的宫主会想要我的命？……哈哈，你可知道现在车子里的人是谁？","tone":"大笑","chapter":1,"line_start":294,"line_end":296},{"speaker":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","speaker_name":"鸡冠人","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"现在车子里的，不过是移花宫的宫女、丫头，只不过是自移花宫逃出来的叛徒！","tone":"淡然","chapter":1,"line_start":298,"line_end":298},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"江公子又吃惊了吧？江公子只怕还要问，这种事咱们又怎会知道？嘿嘿，这可是件秘密，你可永远也猜不到。","tone":"大笑","chapter":1,"line_start":302,"line_end":304},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_hong_yi_ji_guan","text":"留神！这小子拼上命了！","tone":"厉声","chapter":1,"line_start":322,"line_end":322},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"少妇","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"玉郎，你小心些……只要你小心些，他们绝不是你的敌手！","tone":"担心","chapter":1,"line_start":338,"line_end":338},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":null,"text":"唷，这小子确气不错，居然还是个双胞胎！","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":1,"line_start":340,"line_end":340},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hei_mian_jun","text":"恶贼，滚开！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":1,"line_start":342,"line_end":342},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"少妇","listener":"char_hei_mian_jun","text":"恶贼，你……你……","tone":"愤怒","chapter":1,"line_start":346,"line_end":346},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"小美人儿，你放心，现在我不会对你怎样的，但等你好了，我却要……哈哈，哈哈……","tone":"大笑","chapter":1,"line_start":348,"line_end":350},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hei_mian_jun","text":"恶贼，只要你敢动她……","tone":"愤怒","chapter":1,"line_start":352,"line_end":352},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"我就动她，你又能怎样？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":1,"line_start":354,"line_end":356},{"speaker":"char_che_zhong_nv","speaker_name":"少妇","listener":"char_jiang_feng","text":"玉郎，你小心些！","tone":"颤声","chapter":1,"line_start":360,"line_end":362},{"speaker":"char_hei_mian_jun","speaker_name":"黑面君","listener":"char_che_zhong_nv","text":"你的玉郎就要变成玉鬼了！","tone":"大笑","chapter":1,"line_start":364,"line_end":366},{"speaker":"char_jiang_feng","speaker_name":"江枫","listener":"char_hei_mian_jun","text":"恶贼，我纵成厉鬼，也不饶你！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":1,"line_start":368,"line_end":368}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
